rofile New Year''s Eve event production.', '$8B-$12B range', 'high', 'critical', 'Event producers, content creators, corporate event planners, media production companies', 6, '["On-demand crew marketplace platform connecting vetted camera operators with event producers", "Specialized boutique production agency focused on holiday/peak-season event videography", "Crew booking/staffing service with guaranteed availability guarantee during high-demand periods"]', NULL, '["Highly competitive market with established production companies and freelancer networks already serving this segment", "Seasonal demand concentration creates cash flow and resource utilization challenges", "Single data point (one Craigslist posting) is insufficient to validate actual market size or repeating demand pattern"]', '["Conduct market research analyzing Craigslist and similar platforms for camera crew requests across 6-12 months to identify frequency, geography, and rate patterns", "Interview 10-15 event producers and production companies to quantify crew availability gaps and pricing pain points during peak seasons", "Research existing crew marketplaces (Peerspace, Crewscale, etc.) to understand market saturation, margins, and value differentiation opportunities"]', NULL, 'Event producers and content creators require access to skilled, available camera operators during peak demand periods (holidays, major events) when crews are heavily booked, creating a supply-demand mismatch that limits production quality and project completion.', NULL, 37.7992, -122.4092, NULL, NULL, NULL) ON CONFLICT (id) DO NOTHING;
